direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry: Quality Repo Analysis ---

quality-repo-analysis: |md
  **/quality-repo-analysis**

  - Analyzes CI/CD, test coverage,
    code quality, security, images
  - Scores each dimension 0-10
  - Compares against gold standards
  - Generates HTML + markdown report
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Test Rules Generator ---

test-rules-generator: |md
  **/test-rules-generator**

  - Extracts test patterns from repo
  - Detects unit, mock, E2E, contract
  - Generates .claude/rules/ files
  - Framework-aware (Jest, Cypress, Go)
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Historical Bug Coverage ---

historical-bug-coverage: |md
  **/historical-bug-coverage**

  - Queries Jira for blocker/critical bugs
  - Deep test analysis with assertions
  - Confidence scoring (0-100%)
  - Generates interactive HTML report
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Konflux Build Simulator ---

konflux-build-simulator: |md
  **/konflux-build-simulator**

  - Simulates Konflux build on PRs
  - Phases: static, Docker, runtime,
    module-fed, operator, manifest
  - Generates GH Actions workflows
  - Catches build failures pre-merge
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Risk Assessment ---

risk-assessment: |md
  **/risk-assessment**

  - Extracts PR metadata via gh CLI
  - 4 parallel agents: risk, test,
    impact, cross-repo
  - Aggregates scores and decides
  - Advisory only, never blocks PRs
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- External Services ---

jira: |md
  **Jira**
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

github: |md
  **GitHub**
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

# --- Flow: Quality Analysis Cluster ---

quality-repo-analysis -> test-rules-generator: "gaps in rules"
quality-repo-analysis -> historical-bug-coverage: "coverage gaps"

historical-bug-coverage -> test-rules-generator: "missing test rules"

# --- External Service Edges ---

historical-bug-coverage -> jira: "JQL query"
risk-assessment -> github: "PR metadata"
konflux-build-simulator -> github: "PR validation"
